headline: With ROIC at 19-Year Highs, Is CCL Entering a New Profitability Cycle?
summary: Carnival achieves a ROIC above 13%, a 19-year high, as pricing gains, cost discipline and debt reduction enhance margins and signal a stronger profit cycle ahead.
